          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1662457609673-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Dissolve the <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> in 150ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[250ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>and add the <strong>sultanas</strong>,<strong> capers</strong>,<strong> red wine vinegar</strong>,<strong> chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and<strong> dried basil</strong> – this is your <strong>sultana stock</strong></p>",
