    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add <strong>half </strong>the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped tomatoes </strong>and <strong>sultana stock</strong> and cook for 10 min or until thickened – this is your <strong>tomato sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
