    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash the <strong>cavolo nero</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and chop roughly, removing any tough stalks</p><p>Melt a knob of<strong> butter alternative </strong>in a pot (with a matching lid) and add the <strong>chopped cavolo nero </strong>and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Put the lid on and cook for 2 min or until wilted – this is your <strong>buttery cavolo nero</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
