      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>caponata</strong> alongside the <strong>buttery cavolo nero</strong> with the <strong>garlic bread</strong> to the side</p><p>Season with a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
